OL,3,CJersey Recovery College closes with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FThe Jersey Recovery College (JRC) has
OL,7,Fannounced that it will permanently
OL,8,Fclose with immediate effect.
OL,10,FFounded in 2017, the charity provided
OL,11,Feducation and training opportunities
OL,12,Ffor thousands of local people
OL,13,Fstruggling with their mental health.
OL,15,FHowever, JRC says it must now close
OL,16,Fits doors for good that due to
OL,17,F"ongoing financial pressures".
