OL,3,CJersey Recovery College closes with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FThe College adds: "JRC has worked
OL,7,Ftirelessly to enhance revenue streams
OL,8,Fand has explored a number of
OL,9,Falternative models to ensure
OL,10,Fcontinuity.
OL,12,F"Despite our best efforts, the
OL,13,Fsituation has reached a point where it
OL,14,Fis unsustainable and all potential
OL,15,Foptions have now been exhausted."
OL,17,FWhen it was created, the organisation
OL,18,Freceived partial funding from the
OL,19,FStates of Jersey Mental Health
OL,20,FStrategy.
