OL,3,CJersey Recovery College closes with
OL,4,Cimmediate effect
OL,6,FJRC also recently gained a share of
OL,7,Fthe Ports of Jersey #10,000 Community
OL,8,FBoost scheme but it was not enough to
OL,9,Fsave the charity.
OL,11,FThe College says it has supported
OL,12,Faround 3,000 people since its
OL,13,Finception with 617 residents enrolling
OL,14,Fon courses in 2023, including sessions
OL,15,Fto ease anxiety, psychosis and sleep
OL,16,Fissues.
OL,18,FJRC has apologised for any distress
OL,19,Fits closure may cause and thanks those
OL,20,Fwho have supported the organisation
OL,21,Fthroughout the years.
